-- Bernanke, Geithner to Testify on March 21 on Europe Debt Crisis
-- B y   J o s h u a   Z u m b r u n
-- 2012-03-19T16:46:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-19/bernanke-geithner-to-testify-on-march-21-on-europe-debt-crisis.html
Federal Reserve Chairman  Ben S. Bernanke  and Treasury Secretary Timothy F. Geithner plan to
testify before a U.S. House committee about  Europe ’s debt crisis
on March 21.  They will speak before the House Committee on Oversight and
Government Reform at a hearing scheduled to begin at 9:30 a.m.,
panel spokesman Jeffrey Solsby said today. The hearing is
titled, “Europe’s Sovereign Debt Crisis: Causes, Consequences
for the  United States  and Lessons Learned.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Joshua Zumbrun in Washington at 
 jzumbrun@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christopher Wellisz at 
 cwellisz@bloomberg.net  